buy this stupid nostrum.

760
00:39:49,600 --> 00:39:51,568
It's a health mixture.

761
00:39:51,640 --> 00:39:54,450
Sulfur, molasses
and barley extract.

762
00:39:54,520 --> 00:39:56,727
STANLEY: It's disgusting
and is of no proven value.

