00:42:29,200 --> 00:42:30,440
Mmm.

822
00:42:32,120 --> 00:42:33,645
Yes.

823
00:42:33,920 --> 00:42:34,921
Mmm.

824
00:42:36,560 --> 00:42:38,961
I'm receiving a...

825
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:40,326
It's cloudy.

