I put the entire
engine back together,

883
00:44:59,440 --> 00:45:00,930
and I still have
these two pieces.

884
00:45:01,000 --> 00:45:03,401
This doesn't
make any sense.

885
00:45:03,480 --> 00:45:04,925
If I can just get
these back into here...

