00:45:14,480 --> 00:45:15,720
(THUNDER RUMBLING)
It's raining.

894
00:45:15,760 --> 00:45:16,841
No, please just
give me a minute.

895
00:45:16,960 --> 00:45:18,450
Stanley, come on... If I
can only put this in here.

896
00:45:18,560 --> 00:45:20,767
We have to put the top up.
Come here! All right.

897
00:45:20,840 --> 00:45:23,002
You can't put the top up
without taking this off.

898
00:45:23,080 --> 00:45:24,366
What? How are you gonna
do it without the...

