00:45:25,680 --> 00:45:27,284
Okay, lift! Pull!

901
00:45:27,320 --> 00:45:29,084
It's stuck, it's stuck!
All right.

902
00:45:29,160 --> 00:45:30,924
No, don't do that. You'll
break it, you'll break it...

903
00:45:31,040 --> 00:45:32,644
It's lightning, it's lightning.
We'll be killed.

904
00:45:32,680 --> 00:45:34,569
