905
00:45:34,640 --> 00:45:35,926
Get under the car!

906
00:45:36,000 --> 00:45:37,240
God, I don't want
to go under the car!

907
00:45:37,320 --> 00:45:38,970
It's fine. It's on
four rubber wheels!

908
00:45:39,040 --> 00:45:40,565
It can't get
struck by lightning!

909
00:45:40,640 --> 00:45:42,290
Just go under there!
No!

910
00:45:43,800 --> 00:45:45,006
Oh, we're gonna die!

911
00:45:45,080 --> 00:45:47,162
Run! Run!
Run?

912
00:45:50,880 --> 00:45:52,325
Stanley!

913
00:45:54,000 --> 00:45:55,445
Come now, I've got you.

914
00:45:55,520 --> 00:45:57,249
I've got you.
Okay.

915
00:45:57,320 --> 00:45:58,651
Oh, my God.
Oh, God, we're gonna die.

916
00:45:58,720 --> 00:46:00,404
I know this place!
What?

917
00:46:00,480 --> 00:46:01,641
I can...
I know this place!

918
00:46:01,720 --> 00:46:03,051
How?
We can go in there.

919
00:46:03,120 --> 00:46:04,963
Let's run! Go!
Come on.

920
00:46:05,040 --> 00:46:06,804
Will it be open?
Well, it'll be open!

921
00:46:06,880 --> 00:46:09,690
It always
used to be open.

922
00:46:10,920 --> 00:46:12,490
STANLEY: Goodness! I found
that rather exhilarating.

923
00:46:12,600 --> 00:46:14,125
SOPHIE: Did you see that lightning?
(THUNDER RUMBLING)

924
00:46:14,200 --> 00:46:15,486
Goodness me.

925
00:46:15,640 --> 00:46:16,880
I can't believe
I found this place.

926
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:18,411
What is this?
It's an observatory.

927
00:46:18,480 --> 00:46:19,720
I came here as a boy.

928
00:46:19,880 --> 00:46:21,166
Oh, thank God
we found it.

929
00:46:21,240 --> 00:46:23,083
We just got a little wet.
It's water.

930
00:46:23,160 --> 00:46:25,288
Are you kidding? We could've
been struck by lightning.

931
00:46:25,360 --> 00:46:28,091
We could die of pneumonia.

932
00:46:28,160 --> 00:46:29,810
I'm sure your fiancée
wouldn't be too pleased.

933
00:46:29,880 --> 00:46:32,360
Well, this would never have
happened if Olivia was here.

934
00:46:32,440 --> 00:46:33,805
Oh, no?

935
00:46:33,880 --> 00:46:35,370
Um, she's, uh,
too competent.

936
00:46:35,480 --> 00:46:37,050
She'd have fixed the car.

937
00:46:37,120 --> 00:46:38,690
Is she also a mechanic?

938
00:46:38,760 --> 00:46:41,127
Well, she's one of those people
who's good at everything.

939
00:46:41,200 --> 00:46:42,326
How lucky for you.

940
00:46:42,400 --> 00:46:43,845
Yes, yes.
That's...

941
00:46:43,920 --> 00:46:45,649
I suppose so.

942
00:46:50,040 --> 00:46:51,405
What are you staring at?

943
00:46:52,440 --> 00:46:55,489
You have no idea how
miserable you look.

944
00:46:55,720 --> 00:46:56,846
(CHUCKLES)

945
00:46:56,920 --> 00:47:00,288
I'm freezing.
I mean, the...

946
00:47:00,360 --> 00:47:02,567
Can you hold me,
or something?

947
00:47:02,640 --> 00:47:04,290
I can offer you
my waistcoat.

948
00:47:04,360 --> 00:47:05,805
No, you're wetter
than I am.

949
00:47:05,880 --> 00:47:08,121
Just put an arm
around me, or you know...

950
00:47:08,200 --> 00:47:10,282
Body heat, it's...

